---
import LeafletMap from "../components/LeafletMap.astro";
import CloseButton from "../assets/close-button.svg";
import CloseButtonSmall from "../assets/close-button-small.svg";
import "../styles/travel-map.css";
---

<div class="travel-map-container">
  <div id="BAModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Buenos Aires</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          this is the capital city of my country!! i haven't really spent a lot
          of time here since most of the times i've been here were for paperwork
          stuff or going to the airport lol
        </p>
        <p>regardless of that it's a pretty nice city!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="vcpModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Villa Carlos Paz</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          really nice touristic city in c√≥rdoba! i don't really have a lot of
          pictures and landscape wise it's not the most impressing city but it's
          a fun city to go to on like a weekend trip :D
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="bariModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Bariloche</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          beautiful city on southern argentina! it's been a long time since i've
          been here but regardless of that it has beautiful landscapes and views
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="santiagoModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Santiago del Estero</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          i've only been here once and it's because we had to sleep during a
          roadtrip so it wasn't really a planned trip. it's just a regular city
          not really much to say about it, i don't think i even have pictures of
          it lol
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="tafiModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Taf√≠ del Valle</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          i've been here on a roadtrip across northern argentina! the town
          itself is really small but the views are really really nice, it's a
          little hard to breathe because of the altitude though haha
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="cafayateModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Cafayate</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          stopped here on a roadtrip to have something to eat, didn't really go
          around town much. i can say i had some really good empanadas here
          though lmao
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="saltaModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Salta</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          largest city we stopped at during our roadtrip across northern
          argentina! to be honest the city wasn't that nice, like we were
          expecting it to be something else and it was just a regular city like
          any other, we did go to a few museums and cultural landmarks though so
          that's neat
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="purmaModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Purmamarca</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          last stop in our roadtrip before heading back home!! the town itself
          was super small but it had some amazing views, though if i'm being
          honest it was pretty boring spending 3 days without internet, too
          peaceful for me lol
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="rosarioModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Rosario</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          this is the largest city in my province, i've only been here like once
          or twice and it was just a school trip iirc
        </p>
        <p>
          not much to say about it, most remarkable thing in here is the flag
          monument i guess lol
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="iguazuModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Foz do Igua√ßu</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          we stopped in this city to visit the iguazu falls in the border
          between brazil and argentina!! they're really beautiful, we visited
          both brazil's and argentina's national parks
        </p>
        <p>
          only bad thing is we spent like a week here and there wasn't much to
          do apart from visiting the falls so we went back home earlier
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="vgbModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Villa Gral. Belgrano</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          nice touristic town 80km south of c√≥rdoba city, we've been here with
          my family a lot of times but most of them were when i was younger so i
          don't really remember much. i do know i took my first steps here so
          that's cool :D
        </p>
        <p>
          the town overall has a lot of german influence in the architecture and
          culture, and i know that they host an oktoberfest beer party or
          something like that every year
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="cancunModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Canc√∫n</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          we've been here a couple of times with my family on vacation, it's
          been a couple of years since we've last went so i don't remember much
          if i'm being honest last time i've been here i was 12 years old
        </p>
        <p>
          i do remember we went to a few parks and excursions and stuff like
          that though it was really fun!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="orlandoModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Orlando</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          we've been here once to visit disneyworld and universal! we got to
          visit all 4 main disney parks and the two universal orlando parks
        </p>
        <p>
          it was a lot of fun!! we didn't get a lot of sleep because we had to
          go to each park one day after another but regardless of that it was
          really fun :3
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="LAModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Los Angeles</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          first stop on our west coast roadtrip!! we went around the city and
          visited the warner bros studios, the griffith observatory, the walk of
          fame and a wax museum in hollywood and a bunch of other places
        </p>
        <p>
          the city was really nice except for the smell and the traffic but
          other than that we had a really good time here!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="SFModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">San Francisco</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          last city on our west coast roadtrip before we headed back to LAX!
          really nice city i loved it here!!
        </p>
        <p>
          we went to pier 39, crossed the golden gate bridge, visited alamo
          square and the golden gate park, took a ferry to alcatraz island, we
          also went to ghiardelli's chocolate or whatever it's called, and a few
          more places but i can't remember rn lol
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="miamiModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Miami</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          i've only been here once for a few days after visiting orlando, we
          spent most of those days hanging out at the beach
        </p>
        <p>
          if i'm being honest i got a little bored because the beach isn't
          really my thing but it was nice to visit anyways :D
        </p>
        <p>
          also flights from argentina to miami are really cheap so that's nice
          lol
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="LVModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Las Vegas</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          second stop on our roadtrip!! it was really impressing to see all the
          lights and buildings after driving through the desert for like 3 hours
          straight
        </p>
        <p>
          we had a really good time here! we went to see the cirque du soleil
          show and also went to the sphere
        </p>
        <p>we didn't go to any casinos though we don't gamble lol</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="grandCanyonModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Grand Canyon</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          we visited the grand canyon while we were staying at las vegas, it was
          like a 5 hour drive iirc
        </p>
        <p>
          the views were really nice but it was super cold and full of snow we
          headed back to las vegas after like half an hour lol
        </p>
        <p>
          oh also we saw some deer in the snow on our way out!! that was really
          cute :3
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="sequoiaModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Sequoia National Park</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>tallest tree in the world! not much more to say about it haha</p>
        <p>
          we couldn't even fit the entire tree in a picture without using 0.5 it
          really was taller than i expected
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="yosemiteModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Yosemite National Park</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          beautiful landscape! we spent a couple of hours going around the park
          and the views got better the more we walked
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="bassLakeModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Bass Lake</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          nice little town in central california. we stayed here because it was
          near yosemite and the sequoia national park
        </p>
        <p>
          we didn't spend a lot of time in the town itself but we did visit the
          lake, that was pretty nice
        </p>
        <p>
          also there were a lot of bear pawprints near the lake!! that was
          really cute. we didn't get to see any actual bears though sadly
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="montereyModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Monterey</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          we stopped here on our way back to LAX from SF! we only visited the
          pier though
        </p>
        <p>to be honest there's not much to say about it lol</p>
        <p>
          the restaurant we had lunch at in the pier was really nice yall should
          go there
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="DVModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <h1 class="title">Death Valley National Park</h1>
        <div class="title-bar-buttons">
          <CloseButton class="travel-close-btn" />
          <CloseButtonSmall class="travel-close-btn-small" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-container">
        <p>
          on our way to bass lake from las vegas we decided to go through here
        </p>
        <p>
          tbh i wouldn't go here again sure the place is nice and all but we
          literally had to drive like 5 hours straight through the desert with
          no coverage or gas stations or anything at all and it was super hot üò≠
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <LeafletMap />
</div>
<script>
  const closeBtn = document.getElementsByClassName("travel-close-btn");
  const closeBtnSmall = document.getElementsByClassName(
    "travel-close-btn-small"
  );
  for (let i = 0; i < closeBtn.length; i++) {
    closeBtn[i].addEventListener("click", () => {
      closeBtn[
        i
      ].parentElement!.parentElement!.parentElement!.parentElement!.style.display =
        "none";
    });
  }
  for (let i = 0; i < closeBtnSmall.length; i++) {
    closeBtnSmall[i].addEventListener("click", () => {
      closeBtnSmall[
        i
      ].parentElement!.parentElement!.parentElement!.parentElement!.style.display =
        "none";
    });
  }
</script>
